race.description: Lawrence & Hanson Super Mdn Showcase Handicap
race.comment: TRIBBIANI (5) massive improver at his second run back when attacked the line to finish second over 1120m at Lismore. Gets the right setup and will appreciate the weight drop. CONFORMITY (7) Deep Field filly from a Fastnet Rock mare on debut for the Tony Gollan yard. Ran third in her latest trial over 1000m at Doomben. In leading stable and kicks off in the right race. THE ROOKIE (11) returned for the new yard with a gritty on-pace second over 800m at Kilcoy. Clearly come back in good order and can surprise some of her more fancied rivals. ABSOLUTELYSMASHING (2) resumes. Showed good early speed on debut when a respectable second over 1100m at Ipswich. Expected to come back stronger and must be kept safe.
